    "_string": "Warforge is an app developed and operated by Las Vegas Sands Corp.—the world's largest gaming company—in 2012. It has since been launched and is currently operational in numerous countries worldwide. The app primarily features Texas Hold’em, World Cup-themed events, and high-stakes tournament formats. It has maintained fair, transparent, secure, and stable operations consistently since its inception. Warforge is backed by a robust customer support and after-sales service team available 24/7 to assist users. Las Vegas Sands Corp., headquartered in Paradise, Nevada, is one of the world’s largest casino and hotel operators, with extensive investments across the globe. We are committed to delivering the best possible user experience through exceptional service and the most secure platform.   ",
